# Spicy Mint and Garlic Sauce

::: tip
Tastes amazing on lamb chops.
:::

## Ingredients
* 2 tbsp olive oil
* 3 cloves garlic
* 1 tbsp rice vinegar
* 2 tbsp soy sauce
* 1 tbsp sesame oil
* 1/2 tsp red chili flakes
* 2 tbsp mint chopped

## Procedure
1. Chop up your mint
2. combine all ingredients in a lidded container
3. Shake the container vigorously to mix.
